(@p38, @p39, @p40, @p41, @p42, 1)) AS i ([ChangeDate], [ChangeType], [Quantity], [UserId], [VehicleId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([ChangeDate], [ChangeType], [Quantity], [UserId], [VehicleId])
VALUES (i.[ChangeDate], i.[ChangeType], i.[Quantity], i.[UserId], i.[VehicleId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[StockHistoryId], i._Position;
